reviews.text: Amazing service!!!. We stayed for a night as we were transiting through Hong Kong. We stayed on the executive floor in a room overlooking Victoria peak. The room was nice with separate bathtub and shower and very spacious. My only issue with my stay is that the executive lounge is a bit on the small side given the size of the hotel. The service was amazing throughout though.
Great service! Rooms and public areas are a little dated but maintained really well. Convenient location with Admiralty Station just below the complex.

The staff and the facilities were excellent.   We enjoyed the pool, health club and found the whole hotel, beautiful and clean.  I would highly recommend this hotel.  Also the location was close to the Harbor and public transportation

Received complimentary upgrade to high-floor deluxe room with harbor view, executive lounge access and late checkout as a diamond member. Nice staff, great view and perfect location. Will stay here again on my next visit.

Quite luxurious but a little bit old now. Location is good. Very close to Admiralty station and also close to Central. It is my second time to stay here. If I have any chance to visit Hong Kong again, I would stay here again.

reviews.text: 超靚5⭐
中菜出色美味😋

Amazing service!!!. We stayed for a night as we were transiting through Hong Kong. We stayed on the executive floor in a room overlooking Victoria peak. The room was nice with separate bathtub and shower and very spacious. My only issue with my stay is that the executive lounge is a bit on the small side given the size of the hotel. The service was amazing throughout though.

오션뷰가 매우 멋지다. 수영장은 크진 않지만 가볍게 수영하기 괜찮은 사이즈다.
조식도 매우 훌륭하고 59층 라운지 이용시 에프터눈 티와 이브닝 카테일을 즐길 수 있어 만족스럽다
제일 장점은 호텔과 퍼시픽플레이스와 연결 되어 쇼핑도 편안하게 할 수 있고 쉑쉑버거 영화관 다양한 식당이 있어 매우 좋은 장소이다
홍콩역에서 호텔까지 택시로 10분 내외 이며 캐리어 포함 약 40홍달 정도이다
今天來港麗酒店的Garden Cafe吃自助午餐，一出電梯往左望，蘭花轉了白色，雖然沒有先前的桃紅色那麽搶眼，但卻耳目一新，好有新鮮感。跟着享用自助午餐，價錢是$398+10%，有龍蝦、長腳蟹，都算過得去啦！不過，座位编排得頗密，如果坐在最入的位置，出入也頗為不便。而有一件事值得提提的，就是叫了杯熱啡，但郤伴以凍奶，这點就有點那個了！！
